<p>Users of the type <strong>Back end</strong> can only access limited areas and menus in the plentymarkets back end. Thus, their access to the system is limited. If users of this type should be able to work with roles, statuses and types in the ticket system, a user of the type <strong>Admin</strong> has to assign at least the rights listed in <a href="#table-rights-ticket-system-roles-status-types">Table 3</a> to users of the type <strong>Back end</strong>.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Assigning rights for back end users:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Settings » User » Rights » User</strong>.<br></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Use the search function (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>) and open the account that should be edited.</p>
</li>
