<h3 id="2720">8.2. Creating an FAQ</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Now create the FAQs in the <strong>New FAQ</strong> tab.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating an FAQ:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
