<h2 id="3400">15. Searching for tickets</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Various entry fields and filters are available in the ticket search in the <strong>Tickets</strong> tab. They help you narrow down the list of tickets to find the exact ones that you are looking for. Expand the <strong>Search</strong> area to select further filters and entry fields. This allows to search for your tickets even more detailed.</p>
</div>
